        </item>
        <item>
            <title>全新 Mercedes-Benz CLA 到港，新外型設計 + 可選配杜比全景聲音樂</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/mercedes-benz-cla-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mercedes-benz-cla-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/02/mercedes-benz-cla-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 02 Oct 2023 02:57:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[車壇動向]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1196845</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>平治 CLA Coupé 採用新設計前泵把、星徽圖案鬼面罩和後導流器，令其運動個性更強烈，標準配置 LED High Performance 頭燈和 LED 尾燈亦帶來新設計。新版本增加 Hyper Blue (CLA 獨有) 和 Spectral Blue 車身顏色。全新 CLA 標準配置低風阻、高光澤 18 吋五輻式 tremolite grey 輪圈，另有三種輪圈設計作選擇，尺寸可達 19 吋。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196859" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0012.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>高科技車廂提供新顏色和飾條配搭</h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 配備新一代 Nappa 軚環，並提供碳纖維樣式、石灰木或啡色微纖維等飾條設計。 標準配置 ARTICO 人造皮革/ MICROCUT 微纖維的立體剪裁運動座椅，提供共五種車廂顏色選，擇: 黑色、啡色、鼠尾草灰、鈦金屬灰/黑和新配搭紅/黑雙色。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196852" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>標準設備更齊全，可選組合更精簡<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 標準設備已經包括真皮軚盤，LED 頭，燈，高燈輔助系統，後泊車鏡頭、USB 組合、泊車組合和後視鏡組合。 車身顏色、車廂顏色、飾件和輪圈等，仍可單獨選擇。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>最新一代 MBUX 及 Burmester 音響連杜比全景聲</h2><p>全新 CLA Coupé 採用了最新一代的 MBUX 「經典」提供齊全的駕駛資訊，「運動」配有搶眼的轉數表，而「簡約」只顯示最基本資訊。 結合導航、駕駛輔助和服務模式及七種背景顏色，駕駛者可為儀錶及中央屏幕作多種個人化設定。CLA Coupé 增加了 USB-C 插，頭，亦提高了 USB 充電功率。 所有 USB 插頭現在都會發光。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p>當啟用 Mercedes me app 網上服務後，新一代 MBUX 語音輔助系統在對話和學習能力上均會有所提昇。例如部份指令毋須講 &#8220;Hey Mercedes」 便能執行。 MBUX 語音輔助系統亦能解釋部份車上功能。可選配的 Burmester 環迴音響系統聯同最新一代的 MBUX ，提供杜比全景聲 (Dolby Atmos) 聽覺享受，為音樂提供更多空間感、清晰度和深度。全新 CLA 加強了安全輔助系統，而且新一代泊車組合支援平衡 (S 位) 泊車，亦提供 360 度影像。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>電氣化驅動系統<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新 CLA 200 中的 1.3 升四汽缸引擎 (最大馬力 163 匹) 已作電氣化，並與七速雙離合器波箱配合。輕混能系統包括 48 伏特的電力系統，為皮帶驅動的起動發電機供電。 其短暫可用的 14 匹額外馬力及 150 牛頓米扭力，令起步更敏捷。 起動發電機還提高了舒適度: 除了減低引擎啟動時，的震動和噪音外，它還容許關閉引擎時滑行。它還可在制動和加速過程中回收動能，為 12 伏特，電力系統和 48 伏特電池充電，在加速時提供動力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0015.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>售價<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>全新平治 CLA 200 現於 Mercedes-Benz Lab (新界大圍車公廟路 18 號圍方 2 樓 201 號舖) 公開展示，售價由 $438,800 起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1196862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
